title: Mark Hamill stops traffic with Hollywood star
text:
Mark Hamill stops traffic with Hollywood star 12:42am GMT - 01:51 
Hundreds gathered in Hollywood to watch 'Star Wars' actor Mark Hamill get his Walk of Fame star, causing Hollywood Boulevard to be temporarily shut down. Rough Cut - no reporter narration. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
